----------------------------------
plasmalogin display manager configuration
----------------------------------

:Date: August 2014
:Version: plasmalogin @PLASMALOGIN_VERSION_STRING@
:Manual section: 5
:Manual group: plasmalogin

SYNOPSIS
========

~plasmalogin/state.conf

DESCRIPTION
===========

This file carries state configuration for the plasmalogin display manager **plasmalogin**\(1\).

OPTIONS
=======

All options are configured in the [Last] section:

`Session=`
	Name of the session file of the last session selected.
	This session will be preselected when the login screen shows up.
	Default value is empty.

`User=`
	Name of last logged-in user. This username will be
	preselected/shown when the login screen shows up.
	Default value is empty.

